1. *Uplašena* devojčica je pritrčala mami u zagrljaj. (The scared girl ran to her mother for a hug.)
2. Čovek je video *uplašenu* ženu koja je trčala glavnom ulicom. (The man saw the scared woman who was running down the main street.)
3. *Uplašeni* vlasnik je pustio psa da se brani. (The scared owner let the dog defend itself.)
4. *Uplašeno* dete je stajalo, ne znajući šta da uradi. (The scared child stood there, not knowing what to do.)
5. *Uplašena* majka je uzdahnula od olakašanja kada je videla da je njen sin bezbedan. (The scared mother sighed in relief when she saw her son was safe.)